name: kingdom
trans: A kingdom is a land ruled by a king or queen.

name: language
trans: Language is the words people use to communicate.

name: message
trans: A message is information you send or receive.

name: natural
trans: Something natural is made by nature, not by people.

name: observe
trans: To observe means to watch carefully.

name: protect
trans: To protect means to keep something safe.

name: rapid
trans: Rapid means happening very fast.

name: search
trans: To search means to look for something.

name: travel
trans: To travel means to go to another place.

name: useful
trans: Useful means helpful or able to do something well.
